<center><br>
<img src=http://www.mythicalodyssey.i-p.com/peacock.gif><br>
<br>
My dear Olympians, hold this not against Zeus.  For he only delt the justice felt on an action that I wronged the very order of the Olympians. He knew this was one way to open my eyes that it is not my place to rule on certain things that have to do with the Gods.  And do not fear for the Amazons.  They shall endure.  Bless them with your gifts.  And they shall suceed.  And I will return:::<br>
